《'''DAYDREAM'''》是韓國男子樂團[[DAY6|DAY6]]的第二張[[韓語|韓語]]迷你專輯，同時也是前鍵盤手[[任晙赫|晙赫]]退團後，首張以五人組形式發行的作品，由[[JYP娛樂|JYP娛樂]]製作，於2016年3月30日由[[KT_Music|KT Music]]發行，主打歌為〈放手 放手 放手〉。專輯發行首日便登上[[台灣|台灣]]、[[泰國|泰國]]、[[新加坡|新加坡]]、[[菲律賓|菲律賓]]、[[印度尼西亞|印度尼西亞]]的[[iTunes|iTunes]]專輯榜第一名<ref>{{cite web | title = Taiwan iTunes Top 100 Music Albums | url = http://www.hotmusiccharts.com/tw/itunes/albums | publisher = Hot Music Charts | date = 2016-03-30 | accessdate = 2016-03-30 | archivedate = 2016-03-30 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160330155854/http://www.hotmusiccharts.com/tw/itunes/albums }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | title = Philippines iTunes Top 100 Music Albums | url = http://www.apple.com/th/itunes/charts/albums/ | publisher = Hot Music Charts | date = 2016-03-30 | accessdate = 2016-03-30 | archivedate = 2016-03-30 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160330160719/http://www.apple.com/th/itunes/charts/albums/ }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | title = Singapore iTunes Top 100 Music Albums | url = http://www.apple.com/sg/itunes/charts/albums/ | publisher = Hot Music Charts | date = 2016-03-30 | accessdate = 2016-03-30 | archivedate = 2016-03-30 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160330155259/http://www.apple.com/sg/itunes/charts/albums/ }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | title = Indonesia iTunes Top 100 Music Albums | url = http://www.apple.com/id/itunes/charts/albums | publisher = Hot Music Charts | date = 2016-03-30 | accessdate = 2016-03-30 | archivedate = 2016-03-30 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160330160202/http://www.apple.com/id/itunes/charts/albums/ }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | title = Philippines iTunes Top 100 Music Albums | url = http://www.hotmusiccharts.com/ph/itunes/albums | publisher = Hot Music Charts | date = 2016-03-30 | accessdate = 2016-03-30 | archivedate = 2016-03-30 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160330160441/http://www.hotmusiccharts.com/ph/itunes/albums }}</ref>，主打單曲亦登上美國地區Tunes韓國流行音樂單曲榜第三名<ref>{{cite web|title=Top K-Pop Songs Charts on iTunes Store USA|url=http://itopchart.com/us/en/top-songs/k-pop/|website=iTop Chart|accessdate=2017-07-15|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160330181848/http://itopchart.com/us/en/top-songs/k-pop/|archivedate=2016-03-30|language=en|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並被美國[[Billboard|Billboard]]評選為2016年度十大最佳[[K-Pop|K-Pop]]專輯之一。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/events/year-in-music-2016/7633026/best-kpop-albums-2016-critics-picks|title=10 Best K-Pop Albums of 2016: Critic's Picks|publisher=billboard|date=2016-12-22|language=en|accessdate=2016-12-23|archive-date=2016-12-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161224172933/http://www.billboard.com/articles/events/year-in-music-2016/7633026/best-kpop-albums-2016-critics-picks|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==背景==
2016年3月22日，DAY6透過官方[[Instagram|Instagram]]及[[Facebook|Facebook]]專頁公布專輯預告照，透露專輯將於3月30日發行。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.allthatstar.com/tw/view.php?action=5212&postID=225297|title=DAY6新輯預告照公開 夢幻神秘引期待|date=2016-03-23|language=zh|access-date=2016-03-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160404094939/http://www.allthatstar.com/tw/view.php?action=5212&postID=225297|archive-date=2016-04-04|dead-url=yes}}</ref>3月23日，釋出專輯預購網頁，網頁中的專輯介紹資訊透露全部成員均參與了本專輯收錄曲創作，[[姜永晛|Young K]]更參與全部歌曲作詞、作曲及製作。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.facebook.com/jypnation/posts/995287093860182|title=DAY6 <DAYDREAM> Pre-order|date=2016-03-23|publisher=JYP|accessdate=2016-03-23|archive-date=2019-02-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190215220921/https://www.facebook.com/jypnation/posts/995287093860182|dead-url=no}}</ref>3月25日，公開專輯概念照<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.koreastardaily.com/tc/news/75787|title=樂團DAY6即將在30日回歸　專輯概念照釋出|author=Laura|publisher=韓星網|date=2016-03-30|language=zh|accessdate=2016-03-25|archive-date=2016-03-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160330221846/http://www.koreastardaily.com/tc/news/75787|dead-url=no}}</ref>，28日釋出主打歌〈放手 放手 放手〉的MV預告。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://n.yam.com/bntnews/otaku/20160328/20160328629369.html|title=DAY6《Letting Go》MV預告公開 成熟表演震撼人心|publisher=蕃新聞|date=2016-03-28|language=zh|accessdate=2016-03-28|archive-date=2016-04-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160424223829/http://n.yam.com/bntnews/otaku/20160328/20160328629369.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

3月29日晚間透過V App直播Rehearsal studio Live，向歌迷們介紹新專輯歌曲，並首次以五人組形式演唱出道曲〈Congratulations〉及新歌〈放手 放手 放手〉、〈Blood〉，30日零時公開〈放手 放手 放手〉的MV，新專輯音源也同步上線。

==歌曲與歌詞==
主打歌曲〈放手 放手 放手〉由[[姜永晛|Young K]]、[[金元弼|元弼]]參與大部分的詞曲創作<ref>{{cite web|url=http://kpopnerd.com/blog/2016/behind-the-song-day6-letting-go|title=Behind the Song: DAY6 "놓아 놓아 놓아 (Letting Go)"|publisher=kpopnerd|accessdate=2016-03-31|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160410165901/http://kpopnerd.com/blog/2016/behind-the-song-day6-letting-go|archive-date=2016-04-10|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，是一首以[[搖滾|搖滾]]為基底並融合[[R&B|R&B]]元素的[[Emo|Emotional Rock]]歌曲，歌詞講述一個男人為了讓心愛的人能得到幸福，即使心中萬般不捨，也只能選擇放手 ，特別是歌詞寫道「始終深藏我心中的你 但我現在必須放手」，「因為沒有我你才能幸褔」，「明白這點所以故意推開你」強烈表達出與珍愛的人告別時痛徹心扉的感受。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://day6.jype.com/discography.asp?idx=&lng=EN&page=|title=《DAYDREAM》專輯介紹|publisher=DAY6官方網站|accessdate=2016-03-30|language=en|archive-date=2016-03-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160312172710/http://day6.jype.com/discography.asp?idx=&lng=EN&page=|dead-url=no}}</ref>

〈Blood〉由[[Jae|Jae]]、Young K參與作曲作詞，是一首節奏輕快且歐美色彩較濃厚的歌曲，歌詞寫到「You gotta see blood girl
看到血才能滿足的你」靈感取自於韓國人在面臨爭吵或要打架的時候慣用的語句，在韓國，當有人對你做出超越底線的過分舉動時，通常會回問他「我們非要見血不可嗎？」意指「我們有必要鬧到這個地步嗎？」描寫在一段感情裡，對方總是咄咄逼人的態度弄得彼此難以好好相處，即使另外一方努力的想要和好，卻苦尋不著方法，於是原本純粹的愛情在爭吵中逐漸變質並瀕臨破裂。
<ref>{{cite web|url=http://kpopnerd.com/blog/2016/behind-the-song-day6-blood|title=Behind the Song: DAY6 "Blood"|publisher=kpopnerd|accessdate=2016-04-03|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160410165815/http://kpopnerd.com/blog/2016/behind-the-song-day6-blood|archive-date=2016-04-10|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

==宣傳==
此次回歸為了提升團體的認知度，DAY6改變以往只專注公演不上電視節目打歌的宣傳方式，開始積極參加各大電視台音樂放送節目的錄製，同時街頭及Club公演也持續進行<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.ajunews.com/view/20160404092047620|title=[인터뷰] '믿고 듣는' DAY6를 향한 두 번째 발걸음|publisher=ajunews|date=2016-04-04|language=ko|accessdate=2016-04-05|archive-date=2016-04-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160421210005/http://www.ajunews.com/view/20160404092047620|dead-url=no}}</ref>。3月31日於[[Mnet|Mnet]]《[[M!_Countdown|M! Countdown]]》帶來出道以來首個音樂放送舞台<ref>{{cite news|url=http://times.hinet.net/news/17907327|title=DAY6後日出演「M COUNT DOWN」 出道後首登音樂節目|publisher=HiNet新聞|date=2016-03-29|language=zh|access-date=2016-04-05|archive-url=https://archive.fo/20160329183325/http://times.hinet.net/news/17907327|archive-date=2016-03-29|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，4月3日在COEX LIVE PLAZA舉行街頭公演，並透過V App同步直播<ref>{{cite news|url=http://m.post.naver.com/viewer/postView.nhn?volumeNo=3954927&memberNo=29747755|title=DAY6 주말 버스킹 나들이|publisher=naver|date=2016-04-04|language=ko|accessdate=2016-04-05|archive-date=2016-05-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160512175415/http://m.post.naver.com/viewer/postView.nhn?volumeNo=3954927&memberNo=29747755|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

